            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Do not create your own database&lt;/b&gt;: always rely on system&apos;s API!&lt;/span&gt;

